Astellia is a leading provider of network and subscriber intelligence enabling mobile operators to drive business performance. Astellia’s vendor-independent real-time monitoring and troubleshooting solution covers end-to-end 2G, 3G and 4G from radio access to core network. Astellia’s scalable products and expert services address the needs of operators’ full value chain. Astellia has close partnership with more than 200 telecom operators globally. Headquartered in France, Astellia has worldwide presence with offices in New York, Reston, Rio de Janeiro, Prague, Saint Petersburg, Pretoria, Beirut, Singapore and New Delhi.

